            <h4>How to use</h4>
            <h5>1. Edit hosts file</h5>
            <p>Open hosts
            </p>
            <p>Windows:</p>
            <table class="rouge-table">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="rouge-gutter gl">
                            <pre class="lineno">1</pre>
                        </td>
                        <td class="rouge-code">
                            <pre><span class="mi">C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts</span></pre>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>
                Linux/Mac:
            </p>
            <table class="rouge-table">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="rouge-gutter gl">
                            <pre class="lineno">1</pre>
                        </td>
                        <td class="rouge-code">
                            <pre><span class="mi">/etc/hosts</span></pre>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <p>Append this line to the last of the hosts file</p>

            <table class="rouge-table">
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="rouge-gutter gl">
                            <pre class="lineno">1</pre>
                        </td>
                        <td class="rouge-code">
                            <pre><span class="mi">0.0.0.0 account.jetbrains.com</span></pre>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>Don't forget <code class="highlighter-rouge">source /etc/host</code> </p>
            <h5>2. Add key</h5>
            <p>Open your JetBrains product</p>
            <p><code class="highlighter-rouge">Help</code> > <code class="highlighter-rouge">Register...</code></p>
            <p>Put the code to the <code class="highlighter-rouge">Activation code</code> and <code
                    class="highlighter-rouge">OK</code></p>
            <img class="center-image" src="/assets/images/jetbrains/3.jpg" />
